{"tid":539156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義工靠《溏心3》找出基地","createTime":"2018-01-24T10:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T02:26:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e8305363a3da924df405af494cb287c0649c74fc","tid":539156,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:12:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180124/20284102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180124%2F20284102&d=FwDw7Z2ps91hg4DRjL4wAGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=888479ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180124%2F20284102&h=a23d97a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180124/20284102</a><br />\n<br />\n義工靠《溏心3》找出基地<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180124/large/24la2p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180124%2Flarge%2F24la2p11.jpg&h=78cc2a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方搗破元朗錦田兩個「地下養殖場」，據知全靠動物義工花逾年時間追查，但礙於涉事人行事謹慎，不時搬竇而苦無成果；直至早前劇集《溏心風暴3》播映疑將最新基地曝光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n場主上載合照「自爆」<br />\n<br />\n據有份參與的義工稱，多年前接獲線報，懷疑有人在郊野公園設陷阱捕捉穿山甲，經多次追蹤揭發出「地下養殖場」，當中有人為動物界人士，不時在網上發放救貓救狗事迹。義工稱，起初涉事人只主力繁殖豹貓及大蟒蛇，其後連懶猴、水獺等亦有。<br />\n<br />\n動物義工不斷搜集二人的圖片，企圖找出基地，但單憑空地公園的樹木難以追尋。一年多前場主遷入蓮花地，於去年底借出場地予無綫拍攝《溏心風暴3》（圖），該劇早前播出有關寵物火化的劇情，義工認出中央花園的場景，加上場主在網上發放當日與黃宗澤抱住「猴面鷹」的合照，基地終曝光。<br />\n<br />\n■記者郭美華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t開醫院　辦善終　寵物王國一條龍<br />\n要聞 12小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t被捕職員為樂隊Blue Jeans主音子<br />\n要聞 12小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t來歷不明　或帶冠狀病毒<br />\n要聞 12小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t警搗地下養殖場　撿800珍貴動物包括一級瀕危娃娃魚及黑池龜<br />\n要聞 12小時前"},{"pid":"0da16a9b0ea52a10457bef540670007de6688c47","tid":539156,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> TVB有貢獻"},{"pid":"cbff4fb61a96020d12478a46a847c2240ba87151","tid":539156,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0da16a9b0ea52a10457bef540670007de6688c47","tid":539156,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> TVB有貢獻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"得黃宗澤囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f062d2f91d2b64dd0d83b55113ebf456772b672","tid":539156,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b303bd076fa630420d5e5055a39f5aea64f6ea00","tid":539156,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2874657d34e3278fc501085ae90fd0dd9011f97f","tid":539156,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b756118e3b9924d0801eda6eed9dcc12e85ba5","tid":539156,"uid":167124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}